        {
            "title": "來凱醫藥擬回購 管理層亦擬增持 料涉款最多5600萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">來凱醫藥(02105)公布，擬行使回購授權不時在市場回購，另公司高級管理層亦有意增持，估計兩者涉及金額最多5600萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16282964-%e4%be%86%e5%87%b1%e9%86%ab%e8%97%a5%e6%93%ac%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bc-%e7%ae%a1%e7%90%86%e5%b1%a4%e4%ba%a6%e6%93%ac%e5%a2%9e%e6%8c%81-%e6%96%99%e6%b6%89%e6%ac%be%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a5600%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241120_FI_source-web_Laekna-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 08:35:07",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "啟明醫療或引入杭州高新與杭州盈智勤為投資者 最多集資5億人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">啟明醫療(02500)公布，與杭州高新及杭州盈智勤訂立投資條款清單，對方有意與其他潛在投資者認購啟明醫療股份及換股債，涉資最多5億元人民幣。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/02500_WEB_1.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/02500_WEB_1.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公告指出，潛在股份認購每股作價相等於簽署正式交易文件後20個交易日平均收市價，最高不超過2.5元；換股債換股價則為簽署交易文件後20個交易日平均價的1.1倍，最高同樣不超過2.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">啟明醫療上日收市價為1.23元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司擬引入的投資者當中，杭州高新是杭州市濱江區財政局旗下公司，杭州盈智勤則是俞蔚及安吉盈智勤股權投資合夥企業分別持有45%及40%權益的公司。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16282872-%e5%95%9f%e6%98%8e%e9%86%ab%e7%99%82%e6%88%96%e5%bc%95%e5%85%a5%e6%9d%ad%e5%b7%9e%e9%ab%98%e6%96%b0%e8%88%87%e6%9d%ad%e5%b7%9e%e7%9b%88%e6%99%ba%e5%8b%a4%e7%82%ba%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e8%80%85-%e6%9c%80",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/02500_WEB_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 08:31:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "安克創新IPO在港售股超購26.57倍 暗盤低收逾3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">將於今日掛牌的安克創新(00668)公布招股結果，在港公開售股部份獲27.57倍認購，1手中籤率30%；國際配售認購10.24倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：安克創新官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250717_FI_source-web_300866-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：安克創新官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250717_FI_source-web_300866-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：安克創新官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司以99.32元招股，集資46.32億元。該股暗盤輕微低收，輝立交易平台顯示暗盤收報95.5元，較招股價低3.8%；富途交易平台顯示暗盤收報94.55元，較招股價低4.8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16282852-%e5%ae%89%e5%85%8b%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0ipo%e5%9c%a8%e6%b8%af%e5%94%ae%e8%82%a1%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc26-57%e5%80%8d-%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e9%80%be3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250717_FI_source-web_300866-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 08:31:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期越兩萬三高水逾160點 重磅港股ADR齊高收",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時24分升227點或1%，報23,048點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報23,160點，較香港上日現貨收市高279點或1.22%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣440.8元，較上日香港收市高11.03元或2.57%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣96.1元，較上日香港收市高3.23元或3.48%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣69.8元，較上日香港收市高1.31元或1.92%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣103.2元，較上日香港收市高3.94元或3.97%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣22元，較上日香港收市高0.39元或1.78%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣150.3元，較上日香港收市高2.41元或1.63%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣72.4元，較上日香港收市高0.91元或1.28%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣367.5元，較上日香港收市高4.49元或1.24%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣51.4元，較上日香港收市高0.33元或0.64%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.1元，較上日香港收市高0.02元或0.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報22,990點，升143點，較上日恒指收市22,881點，高水109點。科指期貨夜市收報4,510點，較上日科指收市高水38點；國指期貨夜市收報7,582點，較上日國指收市高水24點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16282935-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b6%8a%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%89%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be160%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e9%bd%8a%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 08:31:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日韓股市初段齊跌 日經暫挫逾1,500點 韓股跌約6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華爾街股市昨晚下滑，科股跌勢尤為明顯，半導體巨擘美光股價跌逾10%，日韓股市今早應聲向下。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260209_FI_source-ap_JP-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260209_FI_source-ap_JP-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時22分，日經平均指數已跌1,521點或2.16%，報68,953點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫也跌495點或5.96%，報7,808點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16282904-%e6%97%a5%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%bd%8a%e8%b7%8c-%e6%97%a5%e7%b6%93%e6%9a%ab%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be1500%e9%bb%9e-%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e7%b4%846",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/20260528_FI_source-ap_KS.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 08:26:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "安克創新暗盤中段較招股價低逾6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">安克創新(00668)將於本周四掛牌，成為2026年下半年首隻登場新股。該股暗盤中段暫時表現則未能沖高，暫較招股價低逾6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據輝立交易平台資料，截至下午約5時26分，安克創新暗盤報92.9元，較招股價低6.46%；富途交易平台顯示的暗盤暫報92.65元，也較招股價低6.72%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16271249-%e5%ae%89%e5%85%8b%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e8%bc%83%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%8e%e9%80%be6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/00668.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-30 17:30:56",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "華潤飲料擬斥不逾5.3億元回購",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華潤飲料(02460)公布，董事會決定行使回購授權，動用不超過5.3億元在公開市場回購。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華潤飲料官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240423_FI_02460_source-web_fb.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤飲料官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240423_FI_02460_source-web_fb.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華潤飲料官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事會明表，相信公司目前的財務資源足以支持實施上述回購計劃，同時保持穩健的財務狀況，以支持本集團的業務增長。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事會亦認為，股份的當前成交價格並未反映內在價值及實際業務前景，有關情況是公司購回股份的良機。回購計劃亦反映了董事會對公司前景的信心，以及對提升股東回報的重視。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16271131-%e8%8f%af%e6%bd%a4%e9%a3%b2%e6%96%99%e6%93%ac%e6%96%a5%e4%b8%8d%e9%80%be5-3%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bc",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250728_FI_source-web_02460-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-30 17:11:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "嘉里\"緹外\"成功標售3伙  成交額6.6億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=16263384&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">嘉里(00683)發展的九龍半山豪宅緹外，成功標售3伙，總成交金額達6.6億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">第一個單位第1座2樓B室連裝修分層大宅，實用面積4432方呎，連兩個住宅車位，以2.15億元售出，實用呎價約48511元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">第二個單位為第6座地下A室連裝修花園大宅，實用面積3466方呎，連一個住宅車位，以2億元售出，實用呎價約57703元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">第三個單位為第6座5樓B室分層大宅，實用面積4262方呎，連一個住宅車位，以2.45億元售出，實用呎價約57485元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">項目至今累售52伙，總成交金額衝破154億元，平均成交實用呎價約5.8萬元。項目尚餘10個分層大宅及2個頂層連天台特色大宅待售。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16263384-%e5%98%89%e9%87%8c%e7%b7%b9%e5%a4%96%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%e6%a8%99%e5%94%ae3%e4%bc%99-%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e9%a1%8d6-6%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/pp_new-flat-transaction_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-30 17:06:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "長沙灣喜薈521實呎戶840萬元易手  2015年貨轉手獲利約「1球」",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=16263364&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美聯物業西九龍分行該行新近促成長沙灣喜薈2座高層B室的二手成交，單位實用面積約521平方呎，屬2房間隔，買家以約840萬元承接，實用呎價約16123元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">資料顯示，原業主於2015年8月以約738萬元購入上述單位，持貨約11年，是次轉手帳面獲利約102萬元，升幅約13.8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16263364-%e9%95%b7%e6%b2%99%e7%81%a3%e5%96%9c%e8%96%88521%e5%af%a6%e5%91%8e%e6%88%b6%e4%bb%a5%e7%b4%84840%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%98%93%e6%89%8b-2015%e5%b9%b4%e8%b2%a8%e8%bd%89%e6%89%8b%e7%8d%b2%e5%88%a9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
